tags.name: cross-burger
tags.description: A hamburger button custom element of Cross type.

attributes.name: disabled
attributes.description: When set to true, the internal <button> element is disabled.

attributes.name: pressed
attributes.description: Set to true when element is pressed.

properties.name: direction
properties.description: The animation direction of the icon, left or right.

properties.name: easing
properties.description: A valid `transition-timing-function` CSS value, for example 'ease-out'.

properties.name: distance
properties.description: The vertical distance between the lines. Small (sm), medium (md) or large (lg).

properties.name: duration
properties.description: The duration of the animation. Can be set to zero if no animation is desired.

properties.name: disabled
properties.description: When set to true, the internal <button> element is disabled.

properties.name: label
properties.description: Accessible label set on the internal <button> element for screen readers.

properties.name: pressed
properties.description: Set to true when element is pressed.

properties.name: size
properties.description: Size of the icon. Should be a number between 12 and 48.

events.name: pressed-changed
events.description: Event fired when pressed property changes.
